\title{Root Stability Analysis}
\taxon{section}
\date{2026-04-04}
\tag{stability}
\tag{transclusion}
\meta{description}{Dynamical stability classification of 12 transclusion tree roots}

\import{macros}

\p{Each root is classified by its stability as a dynamical source: out-degree (generative reach), tree size (transitive closure), max depth (chain length), file anchors (live transclusion targets on disk), and hub convergence (does it reach the 5 attractor hubs within depth 2).}

